Package: sywi.duckdb
Title: SYWI DuckLake Connection Wrapper
Version: 0.1.0
Author: SYWI Team <team@sywi.org>
Maintainer: SYWI Team <team@sywi.org>
Description: A wrapper around the duckdb package that automatically configures
    connections to SYWI DuckLake databases. Loads environment variables from
    .env and .env.local files and attaches both local and remote DuckLake
    databases.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
